title: Amaral (José Cabral Correia do)
body:
He was a bachelor of law and held the position of Treasury Delegate among us.

He was elected as a deputy for this archipelago for the legislature of 1905 to 1906.

He was also elected as a deputy for Madeira in August 1910, but the Cortes did not convene.

1905: Election as deputy for the legislature of 1905 to 1906
1910: Election as deputy for Madeira in August 1910
